videoSnippet.title: Happy Birthday Jobava Baadur! - May You Entertain the Chess World for Many Years to Come
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Baadur Jobava (Georgian: ბაადურ ჯობავა; born 26 November 1983) is a Georgian chess grandmaster and three-time Georgian champion (2003, 2007, 2012).

Jobava, Baadur (2644) vs. Naiditsch, Arkadij (2647)
EU-Cup 23rd | Kemer | Round 2.2 | 4 Oct 2007 | ECO: C67 |
